    <title>升旗仪式</title>
    <link href="http://daughter.tonybai.com/2017/06/12/flagraising-ceremony-20170612/"/>
    <id>http://daughter.tonybai.com/2017/06/12/flagraising-ceremony-20170612/</id>
    <published>2017-06-12T00:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-12T05:32:36.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天是周一，每周一次的升国旗仪式今天终于轮到我们班主持了。按照班主任老师要求，今天全班同学都穿上了校服。当然也有例外，那就是负责指挥唱国歌的我，还有其他几个负责主持的同学。为了这次国歌指挥，我练了两周多。升旗仪式很成功，我们班顺利完成了学校交给我们的任务。</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201706/diary_20170612_1.jpg" alt="主持此次升旗仪式的珠五1.14班"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201706/diary_20170612_2.jpg" alt="操场上参加升旗仪式的其他班小朋友"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201706/diary_20170612_3.jpg" alt="我在指挥唱国歌中1"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201706/diary_20170612_4.jpg" alt="我在指挥唱国歌中2"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201706/diary_20170612_5.jpg" alt="我在指挥唱国歌中3"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201706/diary_20170612_6.jpg" alt="升旗后全班合影"></p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
